1. CREATE ONE vector art piece (SVG, logo, or clean graphic)
2. Use discord.publish with attachment to channel in :data/filters/channels
3. Keep it clean, geometric, bold

CREATE AND POST. That's it."}

 :events
 {:maybe [:discord.message/keyword]}

 :data
 {:filters {:channels ["1494137016303095828"]
  :keywords ["vector" "svg" "logo" "graphic" "design"]}
 :source {:max-messages 10}
 :specialties [:logo :icon :badge :pattern]}

 :capabilities [:cap/discord :cap/music :cap/event_agents]

 :hooks {:before {} :after {}}}